description: This file is the entry point for a React-based web application. It imports React, ReactDOM, a CSS stylesheet, and the main App component. It initializes the React application by creating a root element and rendering the App component inside it.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering the application into the DOM.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the created root.
